00:40.373 --> 00:44.640
<i>♪ I've broken my heart so many</i>
<i>times I stopped keeping track ♪</i>

00:44.711 --> 00:48.409
<i>♪ I talk myself in</i>
<i>I talk myself out ♪</i>

00:48.481 --> 00:52.612
<i>♪ I get all worked up</i>
<i>then I let myself down ♪</i>

00:52.685 --> 00:56.213
<i>♪ I tried so very hard</i>
<i>not to lose it ♪</i>

