<i>with a million excuses ♪</i>

01:00.393 --> 01:03.625
<i>♪ I thought I'd thought</i>
<i>of every possibility ♪</i>

01:05.865 --> 01:10.360
<i>♪ And I know someday</i>
<i>that it'll all turn up ♪</i>

01:10.437 --> 01:14.204
<i>♪ You'll make me work</i>
<i>so we can work to work it out ♪</i>

01:14.274 --> 01:19.372
<i>♪ And a promise you keep that I
